South Africa’s State Mining Company to Supply Eskom After Starting Project

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-06-08T06:04:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/south-africa-s-state-mining-company-to-supply-eskom-after-starting-project.html
South Africa ’s state mining company
started its first coal mining project, Susan Shabangu, the mines
minister said.  The African Exploration & Finance Mining Co. will supply
its first coal stockpile to electricity utility Eskom Holdings
Ltd. this month, Shabangu said in an e-mailed copy of speech in
parliament yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
